  <?dbhtml filename="libxv.html"?>

  <title>libxv-&libxv-version;</title>

  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction</title>

    <para>
      libXv provides an X Window System client interface to the XVideo extension
      to the X protocol. The XVideo extension allows for accelerated drawing of
      videos. Hardware adaptors are exposed to clients, which may draw in a
      number of colourspaces, including YUV.
    </para>

